annah Waddingham (Rebecca Welton) and Jeremy Swift (Leslie Higgins) — who had all previously been contracted under Equity, a U.K. acting union. The studio would then have to reach deals with SAG-AFTRA members, including Sudeikis, Hunt (Coach Beard) and Juno Temple (Keeley Jones).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWill you miss \u003cem\u003eTed Lasso\u003c/em\u003e‘s OG Henry? Drop a comment below with your thoughts on the recast.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-component=\"linked-gallery\"\u003e\u003cfigure data-component=\"image\" data-alias=\"\" data-ratio=\"threeByTwo\" data-round=\"false\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\" alt=\"TV Recasts Explained\" height=\"420\" width=\"620\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1 620w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=200%2C135 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=300%2C203 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=148%2C100 148w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=600%2C406 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=276%2C187 276w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=244%2C165 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/tv-recasts-explained-.jpg?w=620\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=140%2C95 140w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/